{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f9c57ca7c5","title":"周恩来就限期收回被抢武器对新疆军区的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33eb84354d","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":2,"articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"军队和军事","id":"6f7a683373","type":"主题"},{"name":"边境地区和少数民族","id":"c0cd6cf1d4","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"fc075fe23d","type":"title","text":"周恩来就限期收回被抢武器对新疆军区的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7d7897a26b","type":"paragraph","text":"〖时间：八点十分〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ae3b047b3a","type":"paragraph","text":"总理办公室周家鼎同志传达总理指示：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9686865539","type":"paragraph","text":"三促最近抢枪很凶，总理让我告诉军区，让郭鹏同志对三促做工作，所抢的武器要限期收回，全部交回，否则要通报全国。这种做法是违反《九 · 五》命令的，是不允许的。限期交回（期限 总理没有讲，请军区考虑），否则要通报全国，一通报，他们就要垮台。据说，三促几次冲击空九军。代表都在这里，有什么问题不能解决？为什么要这样搞？总理说：请军区出面谈。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ea9d6f79d","type":"paragraph","text":"周家鼎同志说：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6da7fd0e75","type":"paragraph","text":"这是总理指示，你就这样转告军区首长。总理要我直接告诉郭鹏同志，请你转告一下。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"f9c57ca7c5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}